           SHORT="ripper allow you to inject routes to RIPv2 routers."
cat << EOF
ripper allow you to inject routes to RIPv2 routers specifying the 
metric associated with them. While the tool is running it sends 
RIPv2 response every 30 seconds to maintain the route up. This 
happens correctly if the route doesen't exist on the router's 
routing table.
EOF
